Benjamin\", \"score\": 0.8844870640592603, \"rank\": 0.12923366792409227, \"text\": \"Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's been a different athlete all season, his confidence growing, and you combine that with his superior speed, and it took him to gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boldon on the rivalry between Benjamin and Warholm: \\\"This may be a changing of the guard because I think Rai Benjamin now has the formula to keep [silver medalist] Karsten Warholm behind him.\\\"\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4494, \"end\": 4502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"score\": 0.8844870640592603, \"rank\": 0.12923366792409227, \"text\": \"Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\"}, {\"begin\": 4569, \"end\": 4581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rai Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\"}, {\"begin\": 4628, \"end\": 4643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karsten Warholm\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boldon on the performance of the U.S. men's 4x100m team: \\\"This is not a repeat, but this is exactly what happened at the 2022 Worlds.\", \"from\": 4658, \"to\": 4791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4691, \"end\": 4695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org